# Exploration: df

## Rounds
  round 0: 189 isolated cumulative, 17 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 189 isolated cumulative, 17 identical in round (refinement)

## Distinguished: 16/16 flags
  15 observed behavior (15 solo, 0 via combination)
  1 error-differentiated only (1 solo, 0 via combination)
  1 behavioral aliases detected

Aliases: -B = --block-size, -H = --si, -P = --portability, -T = --print-type, -a = --all, -h = --human-readable, -i = --inodes, -l = --local, -t = --type, -x = --exclude-type

